Package seng202.group7.analyses

Class GraphUtil

java.lang.Object
seng202.group7.analyses.GraphUtil
public final class GraphUtil
extends java.lang.Object
A set of static utility methods that prepares material for the graph view classes, such as ranking data based on frequency or preparing strings to be displayed as a graph title.
Author:
Sam McMillan, Shaylin Simadari
